      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Drugs, products, or agents that are consumed for pleasure, and that stimulate bodily functions, consciousness, elevate mood, feeling, or cognizance. These may be found in certain foods or plants, and include caffeine, nicotine, and amphetamines.</Note_Text>
